				 </a>
				 <div class="insights">
				 	<h5>Insights</h5>
				 	<p><em>When asked why they used the web app:</em></br>Most people said they used it when they were busy doing other things online.</p>
				 	<p><em>When asked what device they use to access the content:</em></br>Most participants said, just desktop. If they were on their phone or tablet, they just used the native app. </p></br></br>
				 	<p>With the interview results, I was able to validate my assumption that most users want to multi-task when using the web app. They were interested in scaling the video within a desktop context but not necessarily needing it to scale to their mobile device.</p>
