			<h1>Outcomes</h1>
			<p class="text"> Ultimately, the final solution was pretty simple. But it allowed the user to do what they wanted to do in the first place&#8212;scale their video while doing other things. It also leveraged existing HTML capabilities, effectively requiring very little work from the engineering department. </br></br>
			Under budget and user approved, the feature has since been added to the entire suite of apps, including native mobile and tablet versions. It is now the default mode when first opening the app.</p>
